nt-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">*subject to change as per the rules that are to be notified under the Income Tax 1961<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Example-. If entry amount = Rs. 525 (Rs. 500 from deposits &amp; Rs. 25 from cash bonus) &amp; winnings = Rs. 1000, then,<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">- Net Winnings = 1000 - (500-25) = Rs. 475<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">- On withdrawal of Rs. 1000, 30% TDS = Rs. 142.5<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">- Amount credited to bank account = Rs. 857.5<\\/span><\\/span><br><br><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">We recommend that you go through the Government notification attached at the bottom for complete details on this new TDS law.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":null,\"breadcrumb_background_image\":null,\"breadcrumb_background_image_overlay_enabled\":\"yes\",\"header_style\":\"style-1\",\"header_top_sidebar_style\":\"style-1\",\"pre_footer_sidebar_style\":\"style-1\",\"foote