latform fee for access to the Big11India Services charged by Big11India and pre-determined participant\\u2019s contribution towards prize money pool.<br>Subject to these Terms and Conditions, all amounts collected from the User are held in a separate non-interest earning bank Accounts. The said accounts are operated by a third party appointed by Big11India in accordance with Clause 10 of these Terms and Conditions. From these bank accounts, the User can be made to (a) Users (towards their withdrawals), (b) Big11India (towards its Platform Fees) and to (c) Government (towards TDS on Winnings Amount). Big11India receives only its share of the platform Fees through the said Escrow Agent.<br>The Big11India reserves the right to charge a Platform Fee, which would be specified and notified by Big11India on the Contest page, being created on Big11India platform, prior to a User\'s joining of such Contest. The Platform Fee (inclusive of applicable tax thereon) will be debited from the User\\u2019s account balance and Big11India shall issue an invoice for such debit to the User.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">The User may participate in a Contest wherein the User has to contribute a pre-specified contribution towards the Prize Money Pool of such Contest, which will be passed on to the Winner(s) of the Contest after the completion of the Contest as per the terms and conditions of such Contest. It is clarified that Big11India has no right or interest in this Prize Money Pool, and only acts as an intermediary engaged in collecting and distributing the Prize Money Pool in accordance with the Contest terms and conditions. The amount to be paid-in by the User towards the Prize Money Pool would also be debited from the User\\u2019s account balance maintained with the Trustee.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">Any user availing Big11India services are provided with two categories of accounts for the processing and reconciliation of payments: (i) \'Unutilized\' Account, (ii) Winnings Account. It is clarified that in no instance the transfer of any amounts in the User\'s accounts to any other category of account held by the user or any third party account, including a bank account held by a third party. User\'s winnings in any Contest will reflect as credits to the User\'s Winnings Account. User\\u2019s remitting the amount the designated payment gateway shall be credited to User\\u2019s Unutilized Account\\u2019.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">Each time a User participates in any contest on Big11India platform, the pre-designated amount shall be debited in the User\\u2019s account. In debiting amounts from the User\\u2019s accounts towards the pre-designated amount of such user shall be debited from the User\\u2019s Unutilized Account and thereafter, any remaining amount of participation fee shall be debited from the User\\u2019s Winning Account.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">In case there is any amount remaining to be paid by the User in relation to such User\\u2019s participation in any match(s) or Contest(s), the User will be taken to the designated payment gateway to give effect to such payment. In case any amount added by the User through such payment gateway exceeds the remaining amount of the pre-designated amount, the amount in excess shall be transferred to the User\\u2019s \\u2018Unutilized\\u2019 Account and will be available for use in participation in any match(s) or Contest(s) or for withdrawal in accordance with these Terms and Conditions.<br>Debits from the \\u2018Unutilized\\u2019 Account for the purpose of enabling a user\\u2019s participation in a Contest shall be made in order of the date of credit of amounts in the \\u2018Unutilized\\u2019 Account, and accordingly amounts credited into \\u2018Unutilized\\u2019 Account earlier in time shall be debited first.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">A User shall be permitted to withdraw any amounts credited into such User\'s \'Unutilized\' Account for any reason whatsoever by contacting Big11India Customer Support. The minimum amount that can be withdrawn by a User from his\\/her Unutilised Account is Rs. 200 (Two Hundred). All amounts credited into a User\'s \'Unutilized\' Account must be utilised within 335 days of credit. In case any unutilised amount lies in the \'Unutilized\' Account after the completion of 335 days from the date of credit of such amount, Big11India reserves the right to forfeit such unutilised amount, without liability or obligation to pay any compensation to the User.<br>Withdrawal of any amount standing to the User\'s credit in the Winnings Account may be made by way of a request to Big11India but shall occur automatically upon completion of 335 days from the date of credit of such amount in the User\'s Winnings Account. In either case, Big11India shall effect an online transfer to the User\'s bank account on record with Big11India within a commercially reasonable period of time. Such transfer will reflect as a debit to the User\'s Winnings Account. Big11India shall not charge any processing fee for the online transfer of such amount from the Winnings Account to the User\'s bank account on record with Big11India. Users are requested to note that they will be required to provide valid photo identification and address proof documents for proof of identity and address in order for Big11India to process the withdrawal request. The name mentioned on the User\'s photo identification document should correspond with the name provided by the User at the time of registration on Big11India, as well as the name and address existing in the records of the User\'s bank account as provided to Big11India. In the event that no bank account has been registered by the User against such User\'s account with Big11India, or the User has not verified his\\/her User account with Big11India, to Big11India\'s satisfaction and in accordance with these Terms and Conditions, Big11India shall provide such User with a notification to the User\'s email address as on record with Big11India at least 30 days prior to the Auto Transfer Date, and in case the User fails to register a bank account with his\\/her User Account and\\/or to verify his\\/her User Account by the Auto Transfer Date, Big11India shall be entitled to forfeit any amounts subject to transfer on the Auto Transfer Date. Failure to provide Big11India with a valid bank account or valid identification documents (to Big11India\'s satisfaction) may result in the forfeiture of any amounts subject to transfer in accordance with this clause.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">Further, in order to conduct promotional activities, Big11India may gratuitously issue Cash Bonus to the User for the purpose of participation in any Contest(s) and no User shall be permitted to transfer or request the transfer of any amount in to the Cash Bonus. The usage of any Cash Bonus issued shall be subject to the limitations and restrictions, including without limitation, restrictions as to time within which such Cash Bonus must be used, as applied by Big11India and notified to the User at the time of issue of such amount. The issue of any Cash Bonus to the user is subject to the sole discretion of Big11India and cannot be demanded by any User as a matter of right. The issue of any Cash Bonus by Big11India on any day shall not entitle the user to demand the issuance of such Cash Bonus at any subsequent period in time nor create an expectation of recurring issue of such Cash Bonus by Big11India to such User. The Cash Bonus granted to the user may be used by such User for the purpose of setting off against the contribution to prize pool in any Contest, in accordance with these Terms and Conditions. The Cash Bonus shall not be withdraw-able or transferrable to any other account of the User, including the bank account of such User, or of any other User or person, other that as part of the winnings of a User in any Contest(s). In case the User terminates his\\/her account with Big11India or such account if terminated by Big11India, all Cash Bonus granted to the user shall return to Big11India and the User shall not have any right or interest on such points. Users agree that once they confirm a transaction on Big11India they shall be bound by and make payment for that transaction.<br>The User acknowledges that subject to time taken for bank reconciliations and such other external dependencies that Big11India has on third parties, any transactions on Big11India Platform may take up to 24-72 hours to be processed. Any amount paid or transferred into the User\'s \'Unutilized\' Account or Winnings Account may take up to 24-72 hours to reflect in the User\'s \'Unutilized\' Account or Winnings Account balance. Similarly, the utilization of the Cash Bonus or money debited from \'Unutilized\' Account or Winnings Account may take up to 24-72 hours to reflect in the User\'s \'Unutilized\' Account or Winnings Account balance. Users agree not to raise any complaint or claim against Big11India in respect of any delay, including any lost opportunity to join any Contest or match due to delay in crediting of transaction amount into any of the User\'s accounts. A transaction, once confirmed, is final and no cancellation is permissible.<br>Big11India may, in certain exceptional circumstances and at its sole and absolute discretion, refund the amount to the User after deducting applicable cancellation charges and taxes. At the time of the transaction, Users may also be required to take note of certain additional terms and conditions and such additional terms and conditions shall also govern the transaction. To the extent that the additional terms and conditions contain any clause that is conflicting with the present terms and conditions, the additional terms and conditions shall prevail.<br>Big11India shall not charge any processing fee for the First PAYTM wallet transfer of such amount from the Winnings Account to the User\'s PAYTM Wallet account on record with Big11India. 2% processing fee will be charged from the second transaction done through PAYTM Withdrawal.<\\/p><\\/div><div class=\\\"heading\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><h2 style=\\\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(22, 20, 20);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;\\\">Refund Policy<\\/h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">At Big11India we believe Your money is yours &amp; you should get it immediately when you want. We are working with the best banking &amp; payment gateway partners to pay-out our users at the earliest possible. However, all the refunds at Big11India are subject to following conditions:<br>Transaction, once confirmed, is final and no cancellation is permissible. However, Big11India may, at its sole and absolute discretion, permit a Player to cancel a transaction and refund the amount paid:<\\/p><ol class=\\\"lis\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;\\\"><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">If the Player sends a written request to Big11India from the registered email Id to cancel such payment; or<\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">-&nbsp;If the payment is made for participation in the paid versions of the Contests, the cancellation request must be received at least 2 days prior to the commencement of the round in respect of which the payment is made; Big11India shall not be liable to refund any amount thereafter.<br>Big11India may, at its sole and absolute discretion, refund the amount to the Player after deducting applicable cancellation charges and taxes. At the time of the transaction, Players may also be required to take note of certain additional terms and conditions and such additional terms and conditions shall also govern the transaction. To the extent that the additional terms and conditions contain any clause that is conflicting with the present terms and conditions, the additional terms and conditions shall prevail.<br>All the refunds are processed to the same mode \\/ financial instruments through which the deposits were made.<br>In some cases, internal review team may take upto 2 working days to process a Refund. All prizes shall be subject to deduction of tax (\\u201cTDS\\u201d) as per the Income Tax Act 1961. Winners will be provided TDS certificates in respect of such tax deductions. The Winners shall be responsible for payment of any other applicable tax, including but not limited to, income tax, gift tax, etc. in respect of the prize money.<br>Big11India reserves the right to modify\\/change these Payment &amp; Refund terms &amp; conditions anytime without any notice.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol><h5 style=\\\"-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;box-sizing:bor