 of the Contest(s) made available on Big11India platform. Users may participate in the Contest(s) by paying the pre-designated amount as provided on the relevant Contest page. The \\u2018pre-designated amount\\u2019 means and includes pre-determined platform fee for accessing Big11India services and pre-determined participant\'\\u2019s contribution towards prize money pool. The Participant with the highest aggregate points at the end of the pre-determined match shall be eligible to win a pre-designated prize which is disbursed out of prize money pool, as stated on the relevant Contest(s) page.<\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">A Participant may create different Teams for participation in Contest(s) in relation to a Sport Event across the Big11India Services. However, unless Big11India specifies otherwise in relation to any Contest (\\\"\\u201cMultiple Entry Contest\\\"\\u201d), Participants acknowledge and agree that they may enter only one Team in any Contest offered in relation to a Sport Event. In case of Multiple Entry Contest(s), a Participant may enter more than one Team in a single Multiple Entry Contest. In addition, it is expressly clarified that Big11India may, from time to time, restrict the maximum number of Teams that may be created by a single User account (for each format of the contest) or which a single User account may enter in a particular Multiple Entry Contest, in each case to such number as determined by Big11India in its sole discretion.<\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"font-size:15px;margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;\\\">Participant shall pay a pre-designated amount for participating in the contest(s) being created on the Big11India platform. In the event a Participant indicates, while entering an address, that he\\/she is a resident of either Assam,