INSERT INTO `faqs` VALUES (1,'Q-1 What is Big11India?','<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\">Big11India is India\'s most trusted fantasy sports game app. Lowest entry fees guaranteed. We offer all the Cricket Series, Football Series , Basketball Series, Kabaddi series many users playing fantasy </span></span></p>',3,'published','2025-02-28 23:46:06','2025-03-02 05:05:30'),(2,'Q-2 What is Fantasy Cricket ?','<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\">Fantasy cricket is an online game where a user can create a virtual team consisting of real cricket players. The players can be chosen from the upcoming match and points are scored depending on how the selected players perform in that real-life match. The higher your team scores, the better are your chances of winning.</span></span></p>',3,'published','2025-02-28 23:46:06','2025-03-02 05:06:15'),(3,'Q.3 How to play Fantasy Cricket ?','<p><strong style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\">A-3</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"> Playing fantasy cricket on Big11India is very easy. Just follow the steps below.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">a-</strong> Select the match that you wish to play</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">b- </strong>Join one of the many contests</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">c-</strong> Create your team4. Win money and withdraw cash your Bank Account</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span class=\"pr-3 pt-1\" style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">Q-4 </strong></span></span><strong style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\">What are tips and tricks win more?</strong></p>',3,'published','2025-02-28 23:46:06','2025-03-02 05:06:56'),(4,'A-4  A player sitting outside cannot perform So make sure you choose only those players who are going to be in the playing XI.','<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\">But the good thing is that at Big11India, you can now edit your team till the last min before the match starts.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">B-  </strong>Choose players based on their form from previous matches.Selecting a player in form will benefit you more compared to selecting a player who isn\'t. Also, see how a player haves performed against the same opponent or on the same pitch in past matches.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\">Check the pitch &amp; weather report.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">C- </strong> Check if it is a bowling or batting friendly pitch? Is the average score on that pitch above 190 in T20s? This will help you decide if you want to go for a batsmen heavy team or a bowler heavy team.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">D-</strong>  Bowler\'s economy doesnt matter too much. Wickets do So pick your bowlers who are wicket takers. For example, bowlers like Piyush Chawla or Imran Tahir will give you more points, because they take a lot of wickets even if they get hit a lot. Once you have selected your \"Best XI\", it\'s time to choose a captain and a vice-captain for your team.</span></span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">E-</strong> As they say, a captain should lead by example in fantasy cricket, whatever points your captain make will be doubled and your vice-captain will get 1.5 times his points.</span></span></p>',1,'published','2025-02-28 23:46:06','2025-03-02 05:07:43');
