INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (13,'Top Reasons to Choose Big11India, the Best Fantasy Cricket App in India','Top Reasons to Choose Big11India, the Best Fantasy Cricket App in India','<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Fantasy cricket have rapidly grown their popularity in India, with millions of fans participating in the fun of creating their dream teams and fighting for big rewards. In a competitive market with multiple fantasy cricket applications,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;outline:none medium;text-decoration:none;transition:0.3s ease-out;\" href=\"https://www.mymaster11.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Big11India</u></a>&nbsp;stands out as one of the best fantasy cricket apps for people who want to enjoy the game and boost their chances of winning. What stands out Big11India is its low competition, which greatly boosts your chances of winning. In this&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;outline:none medium;text-decoration:none;transition:0.3s ease-out;\" href=\"https://www.mymaster11.com/blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">blog</u></a>, we’ll look at how Big11India’s is the platform to increases your chances of success and why it should be your go-to app for fantasy cricket.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">What Makes Big11India Unique?</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Big11India is a fast and user-friendly fantasy cricket app that allows players to build their own fantasy teams with real-life players from a variety of sports. Whether you’re a fan of cricket, football, or kabaddi,&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;outline:none medium;text-decoration:none;transition:0.3s ease-out;\" href=\"https://www.mymaster11.com/about-us\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">Big11India</u></a>&nbsp;has several kinds of competitions where participants can compete for cash rewards based on their build team performed during actual matches. But what actually sets apart Big11India from other&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:inherit;outline:none medium;text-decoration:none;transition:0.3s ease-out;\" href=\"https://www.mymaster11.com/responsible-play\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">fantasy cricket apps&nbsp;</u></a>vis its focus on delivering a fair and exciting experience for all players, especially beginners.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">This dedication to offering a simple and friendly setting for beginners sets apart Big11India as one of the best fantasy cricket apps for people hoping to begin their fantasy cricket journey without being crowded out by strong competition.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\">Lower competition means higher winning chances:</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">One of the best features of Big11India is its very low competition in contests, especially when compared to other, big fantasy cricket platforms. Many of the more popular apps put you against thousands, if not millions, of other users, making winning extremely challenging. Big11India, on the other hand, provides a less crowded stage with less competitors for each contest. This significantly raises your chances of winning.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Because there is less competition due to a lower number of contestants, your chances of winning are significantly higher, especially if you are new to fantasy cricket. Even if you perform well on larger platforms, you may need to rank higher due to the large number of high-performing player. Big11India allows you to participate in small, more manageable contests, making it a perfect choice for newcomers.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(130, 130, 130);font-family:&quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:var(--tg-body-line-height);margin:20px 0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decora